gomodel:SYNGO_781  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: A total of 296 proteins were identified in a PSD preparation from forebrain or cerebellum by LC-MS/MS. Among these neurocan (CSPG3) was identified.\nAs neurocan is generally described as extracellular matrix components we consider the protein as part of the perisynaptic or synaptic extracellular matrix.\n\n13/10/2017 Pim\n- Since this data concerns High Throughput Data SynGO does not allow inference to a more specific term.. Experimental description: \"PSD fractions were prepared from rat forebrains and cerebellum ...\", p. 1159" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" ;
        dc:date           "2017-10-13" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_781" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

